title: "Analytical types"

Names of Julia types are listed where that analytical type has been implemented in the current version of Tabulae.

- Pronoun
- Adjective
- Adverb
- Finite verb: `LMFFiniteVerb`  
- Infinitive
- Participle
- Supine
- Gerund
- Gerundive
- Uninflected form
